      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Shirish Chinchalkar</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:152px;\"><a href=\"https://www.moodysanalytics.com/about-us/subject-matter-experts/shirish-chinchalkar\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/d/d3/Portrait-chinchalkar-shirish.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Portrait-chinchalkar-shirish.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Shirish Chinchalkar <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Shirish Chinchalkar</b>,<br />\nan <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indian_Americans\">Indian American</a> mathematician, mechanical engineer, computer scientist, and senior analyst at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moody%27s_Investors_Service\">Moody's Investors Service</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nHe holds a Ph.D. in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mechanical_engineering\">mechanical engineering</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cornell_University\">Cornell University</a> and an <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Master_of_Arts\">M.A.</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_finance\">mathematical finance</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_York_University\">New York University</a>, \nand gained experience in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Numerical_analysis\">numerical</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/High-performance_computing\">high-performance computing</a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computational_finance\">computational finance</a>, where he applied <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monte_Carlo_method\">Monte Carlo methods</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_optimization\">numerical optimization</a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parallel_computing\">parallel computing</a> while teaching and researching at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indian_Institute_of_Technology_Bombay\">Indian Institute of Technology Bombay</a> and Cornell University <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Number_of_Chess_Positions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Number of Chess Positions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Number_of_Chess_Positions\">Number of Chess Positions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shirish_Chinchalkar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Number of Chess Positions\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>In 1996, Shirish Chinchalkar determined 10^46.25 as upper bound for the number of reachable <a href=\"/Chess_Position\" title=\"Chess Position\">chess positions</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shirish_Chinchalkar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shirish Chinchalkar</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#TFColeman\" title=\"Mathematician\">Thomas F. Coleman</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/BF01300863\">Parallel structural optimization applied to bone remodeling on distributed memory machines</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/journal/10589\">Computational Optimization and Applications</a>, Vol. 4, No. 4 </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shirish Chinchalkar</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i>An Upper Bound for the Number of Reachable Positions</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#19_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 19, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shirish Chinchalkar</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#TFColeman\" title=\"Mathematician\">Thomas F. Coleman</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#PJMansfield\" title=\"Mathematician\">Peter Mansfield</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ro.ecu.edu.au/ecuworks/4995/\">Cluster Computing for Financial Engineering</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/para/para2004.html#ChinchalkarCM04\">PARA 2004</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shirish Chinchalkar</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#TFColeman\" title=\"Mathematician\">Thomas F. Coleman</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#PJMansfield\" title=\"Mathematician\">Peter Mansfield</a>  (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rd.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/11428848_10\">Financial Computations on Clusters Using Web Services</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/iccS/iccS2005-2.html#ChinchalkarCM05\">ICCS 2005</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shirish_Chinchalkar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.moodysanalytics.com/about-us/subject-matter-experts/shirish-chinchalkar\">Dr. Shirish Chinchalkar | Moody's Analytics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/shirish-chinchalkar-1323a0a/\">Shirish Chinchalkar | LinkedIn</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shirish_Chinchalkar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.moodysanalytics.com/about-us/subject-matter-experts/shirish-chinchalkar\">Dr. Shirish Chinchalkar | Moody's Analytics</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/shirish-chinchalkar-1323a0a/\">Shirish Chinchalkar | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.moodysanalytics.com/about-us/subject-matter-experts/shirish-chinchalkar\">Dr. Shirish Chinchalkar | Moody's Analytics</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shirish Chinchalkar</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i>An Upper Bound for the Number of Reachable Positions</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#19_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 19, No. 3</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/c/Chinchalkar:Shirish.html\">dblp: Shirish Chinchalkar</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301022719\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.015 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.016 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 89/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 198/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion 